holders to lose their investment.

117
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:44.410
They also measure borrowing capacity, the
more debt that you have relative to your

118
00:06:44.410 --> 00:06:49.170
equity, the less likely banks or other
financiers are gonna lend you more money.

