00:07:19.310 --> 00:07:22.050
So this is a more longer term ratio.

129
00:07:22.050 --> 00:07:25.320
So, ratio of long-term debt
to stockholders' equity.

130
00:07:25.320 --> 00:07:27.980
And then finally Long-Term Debt
to Tangible Assets, so

131
00:07:27.980 --> 00:07:31.460
we take Total Long-Term Debt
